684
00:40:37,170 --> 00:40:38,590
I'll send you the password in the chat.

685
00:40:57,990 --> 00:40:58,950
Too cute.

686
00:41:34,330 --> 00:41:35,330
This...

687
00:41:35,910 --> 00:41:37,430
